700641f-b.title: Bronx: Bronx River Avenue - Soundview Avenue
700641f-b.text:
Bronx River Avenue, at Soundview Avenue, Clasons Point,
showing sommer bungalows, part of a colony, on the East River
shore.
August 5, 1935
Views 1, 2, 3
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
